Colombian economist denies cenbank appointment . Mauricio Cardenas , head of Colombia ' s prestigious economic think - tank Fedesarrollo , denied a published report that he had been asked to fill a vacancy on the policy - making board of directors of Colombia ' s central bank . " It ' s not going to happen , " said Cardenas , a highly - respected economist educated at the University of California at Berkeley who served as Development Minister under former president Cesar Gaviria . " The probability of that event occurring is zero , " he added . 
